Date of start of outbreak 2 Feb 2007
Outbreak status: Continuing (or date resolved not submitted)
Epidemiological unit: Village
Species Cattle
Susceptible 60
Cases 4
Deaths 0
Destroyed 0
Slaughtered 0
Affected population Dams 2-3 years old with their calves. Grazing beef cattle.
Summary of outbreaks: Total outbreaks: 2
